source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_SEQ_00<tab>Estrild of the Shiokaze Hostelry remains unwavering in keeping a close, enlisting eye on passersby.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_SEQ_00<tab>Comme à son habitude, Estrild vous sonde du regard.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_001<tab>So good to see you, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. There is news I've been waiting to share with you.

TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_002<tab>It's that damnable Wlveva. She had the gall to chastise me for inviting passersby to join Clan Centurio. All I ever sought was to bring the thrill of the Hunt to all who cared to know it.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_002<tab>C'est Wlveva, elle veut que j'arrête d'inviter du monde au hasard dans notre clan... Si je peux plus envoyer ces pauvres hères à la Chasse, comment je vais faire pour m'amuser<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_003<tab>I grant you, no soul save you that I've recruited has ever reported back from their outings. We assume them all fallen. But such is the nature of the Hunt.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_003<tab>D'accord, les trois quarts de mes recrues connaissent une fin tragique... mais c'est le jeu, <var 08 E905 ((ma bonne dame)) ((mon bon monsieur)) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_004<tab>I've neither time nor patience for the weak. Let the Hunt cull them from our ranks, I say. If a hundred must die for Clan Centurio to find one such as you, so be it. Aye, I knew you to be of great ability. But never did I suspect you would climb so high.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_004<tab>C'est quand même pas ma faute s'ils sont si faibles<var 1D /var>! Ah, heureusement que tu es là pour remonter le niveau... Je te savais plutôt <var 08 E905 ((douée)) ((doué)) /var>, mais je me doutais pas que tu t'illustrerais à ce point.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_005<tab>You've done good by me, and made me proud to call you <var 08 E905 ((sister)) ((brother)) /var>. From this day forth, I recognize you as one of Clan Centurio's most accomplished hunters.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_005<tab>Bon allez, tu l'as mérité<var 1D /var>: je te nomme of<var 16 /var>fi<var 16 /var>ciel<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment <var 08 E905 ((vétérane)) ((vétéran)) /var> du clan Centurio<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_006<tab>With that, you have the Clan's leave to hunt the Far East's most fearsome quarry. I hazard you require no long-winded explanation, having already faced such beasts in Ishgard. Still, for sake of ceremony, go and speak with Wlveva.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_006<tab>Du coup, tu vas avoir le privilège de te frotter à nos contrats d'élite<var 1D /var>! Je sais que tu en as déjà rempli à Ishgard, mais va quand même voir Wlveva, elle te rappellera leur fonc<var 16 /var>tion<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_007<tab>Go well, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. And don't go dying on me now─the true fun has only just begun.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_007<tab>Sur ce, je te souhaite une bonne continuation<var 1D /var>! Et ne meurs pas trop vite, hein<var 1D /var>!♪

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_010<tab>Hail, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. I have had word from Estrild. It seems she has vouched for your promotion to Clan Centurio's elite.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_010<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, j'ai entendu dire qu'Estrild t'avait <var 08 E905 ((promue)) ((promu)) /var> au rang de <var 08 E905 ((vétérane)) ((vétéran)) /var>. Toutes mes félicitations.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_011<tab>I agree, you have proven yourself. There is nary a soul in the Clan who doubts your ability.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_011<tab>Désormais, plus personne n'osera mettre en doute tes capacités, et tu pourras te targuer de faire partie de la crème de la crème du clan Centurio<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_012<tab>Be welcome to our highest rank, <var 08 E905 ((sister)) ((brother)) /var>. We wish you good fortune on your future hunts. And you will need it, for now you hunt the fiercest prey the Far East has to offer.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_012<tab>Ce qui veut également dire qu'à partir d'aujourd'hui, tu auras accès à nos contrats d'élite.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_013<tab>On these hunts, we grade our quarry according to its strength. The higher the grade, the greater the bounty. But, of course, so too the greater the danger.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_013<tab>Leur particularité est d'avoir un rang non pas fixe, mais variable en fonction de la dangerosité de la cible. Évidemment, plus il est élevé et plus les récompenses sont juteuses, mais cela implique également un plus grand risque.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_014<tab>Never has Estrild thought so highly of one of her recruits. You have come far. So far, any further words of warning may be meaningless, but I will give them all the same. Now more than ever, do not overestimate yourself.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_WLVEVA_000_014<tab>Le mot d'ordre est de connaître ses capacités et de ne pas avoir les yeux plus gros que le ventre... Enfin, je ne me fais pas vraiment de souci pour toi. Vu la confiance que t'accorde Estrild, tu devrais t'en sortir haut la main.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>You are now able to undertake elite Veteran Clan mark bills from the Clan Hunt boards in Kugane and Rhalgr's Reach.
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>Vous pouvez désormais remplir les contrats d'élite de vétéran proposés sur les tableaux des contrats du clan de Kugane et de L'Étendue de Rhalgr.

source: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_020<tab>You and I are bonded by the Clan, my <var 08 E905 ((sister)) ((brother)) /var> of the Hunt. I'll not suffer you to die lightly now. Go and speak with Wlveva. The Hunt calls!
target: TEXT_STMBDY108_02939_ESTRILD_000_020<tab>En tant que camarade de même rang, j'aurai qu'un conseil pour toi<var 1D /var>: t'avise pas de mourir bêtement<var 1D /var>! Bon, on fraternisera plus tard. Pour l'instant, fonce voir Wlveva<var 1D /var>!
